WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your “same here” carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags,
we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what truly matters
before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling on
negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.312
=Episode 18=

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:14.520
Dad.

00:01:35.800 --> 00:01:37.440
I didn't mean it.

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:44.680
She wasn't pregnant at all.

00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:48.200
She was lying to you.

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:49.560
Lying to me about what?

00:01:52.360 --> 00:01:53.160
She lied

00:01:54.840 --> 00:01:57.560
to stop you from being
with your brother, right?

00:02:02.080 --> 00:02:02.880
Lu Zhu,

00:02:03.360 --> 00:02:04.280
I never expected you

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:06.240
to become so selfish

00:02:06.240 --> 00:02:06.880
and hopeless.

00:02:06.880 --> 00:02:07.840
Let me tell you.

00:02:11.100 --> 00:02:12.400
The pregnancy isn't what matters.

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:14.000
What matters

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:17.480
is that you pushed your mother
down the stairs.

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:19.360
She's lying in the emergency room
right now.

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:21.400
What matters

00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:22.800
is that you can date anyone

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.360
but not your brother.

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:25.280
What matters

00:02:26.650 --> 00:02:28.690
is that you're eighteen now.

00:02:30.440 --> 00:02:31.440
It's time to grow up.

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.520
Do you understand, child?

00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:34.160
Do you?

00:02:40.720 --> 00:02:43.040
I only have one mother.

00:02:46.640 --> 00:02:48.360
Her name is Shen Qi.

00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:54.200
You betrayed her.

00:02:56.720 --> 00:02:58.400
You cheated with Huang Qingbai

00:02:58.400 --> 00:02:59.920
while she was pregnant.

00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:02.240
You stole my life.

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:04.520
You never treated me like your daughter.

00:03:09.160 --> 00:03:10.360
Lu Jiaming,

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:12.840
the selfish one is you.

00:03:30.520 --> 00:03:31.440
Also,

00:03:35.040 --> 00:03:36.737
I'm nineteen.

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:45.000
Little girl,

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:46.400
it's so late.

00:04:46.400 --> 00:04:47.840
Why are you out here alone?

00:04:48.720 --> 00:04:51.640
My parents are fighting at home.
They're getting a divorce.

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:53.600
I got scared and ran out.

00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:56.120
It's too dark, and I got lost.

00:04:57.880 --> 00:04:59.480
I'll walk you home.

00:05:00.040 --> 00:05:01.720
Tell me your residential area.

00:05:02.200 --> 00:05:04.280
I live at Tianhu International.

00:05:05.200 --> 00:05:06.000
Let's go.

00:05:14.075 --> 00:05:15.435
Do you have a sister?

00:05:17.200 --> 00:05:18.000
Yes.

00:05:18.480 --> 00:05:19.280
I do.

00:05:20.200 --> 00:05:21.800
Is she as pretty as you?

00:05:23.640 --> 00:05:26.800
We look exactly the same.

00:05:27.920 --> 00:05:29.000
We're twins.

00:05:29.640 --> 00:05:33.000
Wow. My mom keeps saying
she wants twins too.

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.320
But not for me,

00:05:34.400 --> 00:05:35.600
for my little brother.

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:37.080
She wants two boys.

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:39.040
You're so lucky, sister.

00:05:39.240 --> 00:05:40.520
Does she treat you well?

00:05:41.040 --> 00:05:41.880
Yes.

00:05:41.880 --> 00:05:43.480
But only for a short while.

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:44.920
Why?

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:46.480
If you have a sister,

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:49.400
shouldn't she always treat you well?

00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:54.440
Because she passed away.

00:05:54.760 --> 00:05:56.440
She's no longer in this world.

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:08.600
Everyone goes through birth,
aging, illness, and death.

00:06:10.320 --> 00:06:12.320
Death isn't the end of a person.

00:06:13.720 --> 00:06:15.640
She's just gone somewhere better.

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.600
I'm sorry, sister.

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:26.880
Don't say sorry.

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:30.000
Never apologize too easily.

00:06:31.440 --> 00:06:32.240
Okay?

00:06:32.880 --> 00:06:33.680
Mm.

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:35.600
Let's go.

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:42.320
You're home.

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:44.612
(Tianhu International)

00:06:44.840 --> 00:06:46.040
Thank you, sister.

00:06:46.120 --> 00:06:48.560
Don't wander around outside
alone this late again.

00:06:49.200 --> 00:06:49.880
Go on.

00:06:50.912 --> 00:06:53.475
(Tianhu International)

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:20.480
Tell me more about them.

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:22.240
Sure.

00:07:22.440 --> 00:07:23.720
What else do you want to know?

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:25.400
Everything.

00:07:26.440 --> 00:07:27.440
Most of all,

00:07:28.320 --> 00:07:29.920
why did Mom do that?

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:33.320
Mom suffered a lot too.

00:07:33.960 --> 00:07:35.760
I hope you won't blame her.

00:07:37.300 --> 00:07:39.920
The man who stayed by her side
during her most beautiful years

00:07:41.200 --> 00:07:42.240
betrayed her

00:07:43.240 --> 00:07:44.800
again and again.

00:07:46.760 --> 00:07:48.400
While she was pregnant,

00:07:49.320 --> 00:07:50.960
Dad was cheating.

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:54.440
Hello, Jiaming.

00:07:54.440 --> 00:07:55.880
Where are you?

00:07:58.440 --> 00:08:00.120
When are you coming back?

00:08:01.880 --> 00:08:03.560
My stomach hurts so much.

00:08:29.925 --> 00:08:31.062
(In operation)

00:08:40.600 --> 00:08:41.960
So adorable.

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:43.320
The two babies.

00:08:45.040 --> 00:08:47.560
Don't touch them. Mind the hygiene.

00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:48.280
Mom,

00:08:49.640 --> 00:08:50.880
take one of them away.

00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:54.800
What do you mean?

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:57.200
Lu Jiaming doesn't deserve this.

00:08:58.160 --> 00:09:00.000
What does that have to do
with the children?

00:09:01.800 --> 00:09:03.840
I don't want them to end up like me.

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:06.480
Trapped in the Lu residence
their whole lives

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:08.200
like caged birds.

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:10.240
I want my child

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:13.040
to fly freely.

00:09:14.800 --> 00:09:16.760
I want Lu Jiaming to taste

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:19.640
the heart-wrenching pain

00:09:19.640 --> 00:09:21.960
of being betrayed.

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:41.120
Qi,

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:42.200
are you alright?

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:43.520
I was worried sick.

00:09:43.530 --> 00:09:45.780
We couldn't get plane tickets
back from Shenzhen, right?

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:48.680
Don't be mad that we're late.

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:50.760
Where are the babies?

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:52.680
Dead.

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:53.880
What?

00:09:56.400 --> 00:09:57.400
One died.

00:09:58.080 --> 00:09:59.000
There's one left.

00:10:09.280 --> 00:10:10.000
Qi,

00:10:10.360 --> 00:10:11.800
well,

00:10:11.800 --> 00:10:12.960
don't be too sad.

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:14.760
Having twins

00:10:14.760 --> 00:10:17.280
is difficult,
and you delivered prematurely.

00:10:17.280 --> 00:10:19.080
Things like this can happen.

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:22.812
At least

00:10:23.720 --> 00:10:25.120
one survived, right?

00:10:25.520 --> 00:10:27.240
How about this?

00:10:27.240 --> 00:10:29.850
When you recover, we can have another one.

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:31.560
Be good.

00:10:33.040 --> 00:10:33.720
Be good.

00:10:35.520 --> 00:10:36.560
Mr. Lu, the flowers.

00:10:57.400 --> 00:10:58.440
Let's get a divorce.

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:02.200
What did you say?

00:11:02.720 --> 00:11:05.080
I said, let's get a divorce.

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:06.880
Qi.

00:11:13.560 --> 00:11:14.240
Qi.

00:11:15.560 --> 00:11:17.400
I know you just gave birth,

00:11:17.400 --> 00:11:18.880
and after what happened,

00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:20.080
your emotions are unstable.

00:11:21.440 --> 00:11:22.160
But

00:11:23.520 --> 00:11:25.120
I hope

00:11:26.240 --> 00:11:28.480
I never hear that again.

00:11:31.640 --> 00:11:33.200
You don't love me.

00:11:36.040 --> 00:11:37.920
Why can't you let me go?

00:11:44.360 --> 00:11:45.480
Be good.

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:48.240
Qi,

00:11:49.520 --> 00:11:50.800
for the rest of your life,

00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:53.720
you can only

00:11:54.560 --> 00:11:56.480
stay by my side, forever.

00:11:59.240 --> 00:11:59.720
Be good.

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:11.040
Flowers.

00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:35.680
Girl.

00:12:35.960 --> 00:12:37.360
My sweetheart is here.

00:12:39.040 --> 00:12:41.160
Didn't you say
you had a surprise for me?

00:12:42.637 --> 00:12:45.080
I lost the goldfish.

00:12:49.880 --> 00:12:50.760
Come here.

00:12:51.760 --> 00:12:53.800
It's okay if the goldfish is lost.

00:12:54.080 --> 00:12:56.040
As long as my precious daughter is here.

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:00.720
Dad.

00:13:00.960 --> 00:13:01.560
Yes?

00:13:02.080 --> 00:13:05.000
Are you afraid of losing Mom and me?

00:13:16.320 --> 00:13:17.400
Of course I am.

00:13:21.560 --> 00:13:23.280
So

00:13:23.280 --> 00:13:24.760
our family

00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:29.320
must stay together forever.

00:13:29.520 --> 00:13:30.320
Never apart.

00:13:36.362 --> 00:13:37.162
Qi,

00:13:37.750 --> 00:13:38.550
I swear,

00:13:39.520 --> 00:13:40.960
no matter what happens,

00:13:41.487 --> 00:13:42.287
don't worry.

00:13:43.080 --> 00:13:44.320
I'll never leave you.

00:13:44.760 --> 00:13:47.240
I'll always protect you.

00:13:47.240 --> 00:13:47.800
Alright?

00:14:46.760 --> 00:14:49.080
(Perhaps until the day you die,)

00:14:49.080 --> 00:14:50.480
(you will never know)

00:14:51.880 --> 00:14:54.360
(that you have another daughter.)

00:14:54.360 --> 00:14:55.880
(Her name is Lu Sun.)

00:14:57.300 --> 00:15:00.520
(She lives within your lies
and betrayals,)

00:15:01.840 --> 00:15:04.520
(carries your hatred and resentment,)

00:15:05.840 --> 00:15:08.600
(grows up in dark rain,)

00:15:08.600 --> 00:15:10.440
(and is unable to sprout.)

00:15:10.440 --> 00:15:12.760
(The only brief love she ever had
came from her sister,)

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:15.000
(who has already)

00:15:16.337 --> 00:15:17.784
(passed away.)

00:15:23.700 --> 00:15:27.475
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:15:27.562 --> 00:15:31.337
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

00:15:31.337 --> 00:15:33.612
♪The you in my memories♪

00:15:33.612 --> 00:15:35.625
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:15:35.625 --> 00:15:39.650
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:15:39.650 --> 00:15:42.737
♪Forget you completely?♪

00:15:42.812 --> 00:15:47.312
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:15:47.537 --> 00:15:51.325
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:55.575
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:15:55.575 --> 00:15:59.712
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:15:59.837 --> 00:16:03.612
